[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說受歲經",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西晉三藏竺法護譯",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聞如是：一時，婆伽婆在羅閱祇迦蘭陀竹園，與大比丘眾俱受歲。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼時，尊者大目揵連告諸比丘：「諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘受歲者，君當說、君當教授、君當教誡、君當愛念，謂第一故。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有人反戾難教與惡法俱，謂梵行者，亦不說、亦不教授、亦不教誡、亦不愛念，彼人謂第一故。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b10_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何，諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b12_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "反戾難教？",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂梵行與俱者，亦不說、亦不教授、亦不教誡、亦不愛念，彼人謂第一故。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b12_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b14_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或一人惡求與惡求俱。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b14_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b15_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂彼人惡求與惡求俱者，此法反戾難教，如是染欲瞋恨慳嫉，不捨諛諂幻，無羞無耻恚結，口言恚結。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b15_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘語已還報其言，比丘語已向多人說，比丘語已而誹說，各各有所說而外說之，瞋恨結而廣與惡知識俱與惡伴俱，不知恩潤、不知反復。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂彼人不知恩潤無反復者，此反戾難教，是為諸賢反戾難教法。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b21_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「謂梵行與俱者，亦不說、亦不教授、亦不教誡、亦不愛念，彼人謂第一故。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b22_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘當自思量。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b24_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂彼人者，惡求與惡求俱，是我所不念；我若惡求與惡求俱，他亦不念我。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘作等觀，當莫惡求，當作是學。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是染欲瞋恨慳嫉，不捨諛諂幻，無羞無恥恚結，口言恚結。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘語已還報其言，比丘語已向多人說，比丘語已而誹說，各各有所說而外說之，瞋恨而廣與惡知識俱與惡伴俱，不知恩潤、不知反復。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842b29_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c03_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂彼人不恩潤無反復者，我所不愛；我若不恩潤、無反復者，他亦不念我。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c03_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘當等觀，當莫為無反復，當學諸賢。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若比丘未受歲，君說、君當教授、君當教誡、君當愛念，謂第一故。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c06_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c07_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c07_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有人無反戾與教法俱，謂梵行與俱者，當為說、當為教授、當為教誡愛念，彼人謂第一故。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c07_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何，諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無反戾與教法俱？",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂梵行與俱者，當為說、當為教授、當為教誡愛念，彼人謂第一故。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或一人無惡求不與惡求俱。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c12_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂，諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼人無惡求不與惡求俱者，此法無反戾，如是不染欲、不瞋恨、不慳嫉，不諛諂幻，不無羞不無恥無恚結，口不言恚結。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘語已不還報言，比丘語已不向多人說，比丘語已不誹說，各各有所說不外之，不瞋恨而廣之，不與惡知識俱不與惡伴俱，不無恩潤不無反復。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂彼人此與教法俱，是為諸賢不反戾與教法俱。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "梵行與俱者，當為說、當為教授、當為教誡愛念，彼人為第一故。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘當自思量。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c22_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂彼人無惡求不與惡求俱者，是我所念；我若無惡求不與惡求俱者，他亦念我。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c22_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘作等觀，當莫惡求，當作是學。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c24_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是不染欲、不瞋恨、不慳嫉，不捨不諛諂幻，不無羞無恥，無恚結，口不言恚結。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c25_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘語已不還報言，比丘語已不向多人說，比丘語已不誹說，各各有所說不外之，不瞋恨而廣之，不與惡知識俱不與惡伴俱，不無恩潤、不無反復。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0842c27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼人不無恩潤、不無反復者，我所愛念；我若不無恩潤，不無反復者，他亦愛念，我比丘作等觀，不無恩潤不無反復，當作是學。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a01_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a04_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘觀已多有所益，我為住惡求與惡求俱，當不惡求與惡求俱？",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a05_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此諸賢比丘觀而知，我住惡求與惡求俱；彼當不喜悅，彼便進欲止。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a06_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a08_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘觀而知，我當不住惡求與惡求俱，彼便喜悅清淨白，佛世尊境界行，見已樂行。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a08_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶若，諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a10_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有眼之士，持極淨鏡自用觀面。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a10_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a11_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有眼之士自見面塵垢便不喜悅，彼便進欲除此垢。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a11_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a12_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有眼之士不自見面有塵垢，彼便悅喜清淨，自見已樂行。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a12_25",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a14_26",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘觀而知，我為住惡求與惡求俱，彼進欲止。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a14_27",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a15_28",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘觀而知，我當不住惡求不與惡求俱，彼便喜悅清淨白，佛世尊境界住，見已樂行。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a15_29",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是住染欲、不住不染欲，如是住瞋恨、不住不瞋恨，如是住慳嫉不捨、不住不慳嫉不捨，如是住諛諂幻、不住不諛諂幻，如是住無羞無恥、不住不無羞不無恥，如是住恚結口言恚結、不住不恚結口言恚結，比丘語已還報其言、不住比丘語已不還報，比丘語已向多人說、不住比丘語已不向多人說，比丘語已而誹說、不住比丘語已不誹說，各各有所說而外說之、不住各各所說不外說之，瞋恨、不住不瞋恨，而廣與惡知識俱與惡伴俱、不住不與惡知識俱不與惡伴俱，不知恩潤不知反復、不住不無恩潤不無反復。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a17_30",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a29_31",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘觀而知，我住不知恩潤、不知反復，彼便不喜悅，彼便進欲止。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843a29_32",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843b02_33",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘觀而知，我住不無恩潤、住不無反復，彼便喜悅清淨白，佛世尊境界行，自見已樂行。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843b02_34",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶若，諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843b04_35",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有眼之士持清淨鏡自照面。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843b04_36",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843b05_37",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有眼之士自見面有塵垢，彼便不喜悅，便進欲止。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843b05_38",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843b06_39",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此有眼之士，不自見面有塵垢，彼即喜悅清淨，自見已樂行。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843b07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843b08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘觀而知，住不恩潤反復，彼便不喜悅即進欲止。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843b08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此諸賢！",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843b09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比丘觀而知，當我住不無恩潤、不無反復，彼便喜悅清淨白，佛世尊境界行。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843b10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自見已樂行，樂行已悅喜，悅喜已身信行，身信行已知安樂，安樂已意定，意定已知如真見如真，知見如真已無厭，無厭已無染，無染已解脫，解脫已得解脫知，生已盡、梵行已成、所作已辦、不受後有，知如真。」",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843b11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "賢者目揵連如是說，彼諸比丘聞尊者目揵連所說，歡喜而樂。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843b17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說受歲經",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843b19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此經，丹藏則名受歲經，而丹有宋無；宋藏則名受新歲經，而宋有丹無。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843b20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "按二經皆云法護譯，名雖少似，義乃大別，則未知其孰是孰非，又何二藏互有無耶？",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843b21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今按《開元錄．重譯錄》中容凾之內，有受歲經，竺法護譯，云與《中阿含經》第二十三卷初同本異譯，〈單譯錄〉中竟凾之內，有新歲經，竺曇無蘭晉云法正譯，注中有云：「《中含》大本無此等經，故編於此。」",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843b23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今撿丹受歲經，與彼《中含》二十三卷大同，則真是容凾重譯受歲經耳。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843b28_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "宋本受新歲經，與彼《中含》全別，而與竟凾名新歲經者，在文雖異，大旨無殊，似是彼經之異譯耳。",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843c01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然今此容凾宋藏受新歲經，與彼竟凾新歲經，以為單譯耶，則何有廣略之殊、譯人之異，又此何編於重譯中耶？",
        "from": "T01n0050_001:0843c03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
